<title>Lyi Algaea</title>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://www.w3schools.com/w3css/4/w3.css">
<link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/favicon.png">
<style>
    body {
      font-family: "Condiment", Condiment, handwriting;
      background-color: #ffffff;
    }

    h1,
    h2,
    h3,
    h4,
    h5,
    h6 {
      font-family: "Playfair Display";
      letter-spacing: 1.6px;
    }

    /* width */
    ::-webkit-scrollbar {
      width: 15px;
    }

    /* Track */
    ::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
      background: #f1f1f1;
    }

    /* Handle */
    ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
      background: #888;
    }

    /* Handle on hover */
    ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover {
      background: #555;
    }

</style>

<body>

  <!-- Navbar (sit on top) -->
  <div class="w3-top" style="background-color: rgb(210, 214, 214);">
    <div class="w3-bar w3-padding w3-card" style="letter-spacing:2px; color: black; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
      <a href="/#home" class="w3-bar-item w3-button" style="font-size: 15px;" >Lyi Algaea</a>
      <div class="w3-right w3-hide-small">
        <a href="/admin" class="w3-bar-item w3-button">Admin</a>
        <a href="/#about" class="w3-bar-item w3-button">About</a>
        <a href="/#menu" class="w3-bar-item w3-button">Recipies</a>
        <a href="<%= loginURL %>" class="w3-bar-item w3-button"><%= loginName %></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Page content -->
  <div class="w3-content" style="max-width:1100px">

    <!-- About Section -->
    <div class="w3-row w3-padding-64" id="about">
      <div class="w3-col m6 w3-padding-large w3-hide-small">
        <img
          src="/algae2.jpg"
          class="w3-round w3-image" alt="Table Setting" width="600" height="750">
      </div>

      <div class="w3-col m6 w3-padding-large">
        <h1 class="w3-center">About Us</h1><br>
        <h5 class="w3-center">Tradition since 1869</h5>
        <p class="w3-large">Lyi Algaea was founded by Mr. Dwight Donato the first. Our origins vary depending on who you ask. We believe we started during the long Alabama summer of 1869, everything was dying from the damned locusts. The food was running out, even the cows because food to the locusts & the family was on the verge of starvation. Mr. Donato did not want to starve to death or resort to cannibalism so he decided to lay down in a shallow puddle and die, instead of dying he inhaled some of the algae and found it sustaining and edible.</p>
        <p class="w3-large w3-hide-medium">This world-famous alga has been passed down from generation to generation from father to brother to wife. Now with almost thirty recipes varying from burgers to stews, our business grows stronger today.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <hr>

    <!-- Menu Section -->
    <div class="w3-row w3-padding-64" id="menu">
      <div class="w3-col l6 w3-padding-large">
        <h1 class="w3-center">Our Recipies</h1><br>
        <h4>Algae Burgers</h4>
        <p class="w3-text-grey">Assortment of fresh algae algae algae and more algae</p><br>

        <h4>Algae Waffle</h4>
        <p class="w3-text-grey">Vanilla flavor with our world-famous algae</p><br>

        <h4>Algae Eggs</h4>
        <p class="w3-text-grey">Scrambled eggs, roasted algae, with green algae</p><br>

        <h4>Algae Noodles</h4>
        <p class="w3-text-grey">Some of the best extruded algae money can buy</p>

		<h4>Algae infused Chicken</h4>
        <p class="w3-text-grey">Chicken + algae</p>
      </div>

      <div class="w3-col l6 w3-padding-large">
        <img src="/algae.jpg"
          class="w3-round w3-image w3-opacity-min" alt="Menu" style="width:100%">
      </div>
    </div>
    <hr>
  </div>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer class="w3-center w3-light-grey" style="padding-top:10;padding-bottom:10;">
    <p>Powered by <a href="https://github.com/Mad-Chicken/" title="W3.CSS" target="_blank" class="w3-hover-text-green">Mad-Chicken</a></p>
    <!-- Shameless plug -->
  </footer>

</body>
